data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom 2 bath brick home on corner lot.  Vaulted ceilings, exposed brick bar, mudroom, covered porch and fenced yard; these are a just a few of the features this property has to offer.  Bedrooms are spacious, open concept living dining area with large 18x20 shop with electric.Mature trees on the property. bring all offers, seller is negotiable. this property is priced to sell fast!
